    "citation" : "Thompson, L.G., T. Yao, M.E. Davis, K.A. Henderson, E. Mosley-Thompson, \r\nP.-N. Lin, J. Beer, H.-A. Synal, J. Cole-Dai, and J.F. Bolzan. 1997. \r\nTropical climate instability: The Last Glacial Cycle from a \r\nQinghai-Tibetan ice core. \r\nScience, Vol. 276, pp. 1821-1825, 20 June 1997.\r\nDOI: 10.1126/science.276.5320.1821 ",
